pgmE - portable graymap Editor
==============================
pgmE is an extremely fast, small and efficient editor which implements the pgm standard.


Getting Started
---------------

  make run                                 Build, run the executable


Features
------------
- load pgm images
- save pgm images
- edit pgm images:
    - median filter
    - gauss operator
    - laplace operator
    - resize
    - rotate
    - threshold operator

